    SELECT [f].[FormFieldsId], [f].[CreatedBy], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[FieldTips], [f].[InputType], [f].[IsRequired], [f].[Label], [f].[Placeholder], [f].[RequestTypeFormStepId], [f].[UpdatedBy], [f].[UpdatedDate], [f].[Width], [f0].[FormSelectOptionsId], [f0].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy0], [f0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [f0].[FormFieldsId] AS [FormFieldsId0], [f0].[OptionName], [f0].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy0], [f0].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0]
    FROM [FormFields] AS [f]
    LEFT JOIN [FormSelectOptions] AS [f0] ON [f].[FormFieldsId] = [f0].[FormFieldsId]
) AS [s] ON [r].[RequestTypeFormStepId] = [s].[RequestTypeFormStepId]
WHERE [r].[RequestTypeId] = @__requestTypeId_0
ORDER BY [r].[RequestTypeFormStepId], [s].[FormFieldsId]

FROM [RequestTypeFormStep] AS [r]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f].[FormFieldsId], [f].[CreatedBy], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[FieldTips], [f].[InputType], [f].[IsRequired], [f].[Label], [f].[Placeholder], [f].[RequestTypeFormStepId], [f].[UpdatedBy], [f].[UpdatedDate], [f].[Width], [f0].[FormSelectOptionsId], [f0].[CreatedBy] AS [CreatedBy0], [f0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [f0].[FormFieldsId] AS [FormFieldsId0], [f0].[OptionName], [f0].[UpdatedBy] AS [UpdatedBy0], [f0].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0]
    FROM [FormFields] AS [f]
    LEFT JOIN [FormSelectOptions] AS [f0] ON [f].[FormFieldsId] = [f0].[FormFieldsId]
) AS [s] ON [r].[RequestTypeFormStepId] = [s].[RequestTypeFormStepId]
